  "body": "There is reference to a function in the spec (phase 0 and 1 it appears) called `ceil_div8`.\r\n\r\nI'll suggest the following definition:\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndef ceil_div8(x: int) -> int:\r\n    return (x + 7) // 8\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe should define it either as a helper or just add this text to the spec so that there is no ambiguity :)",
